// Go workspace root for the Aegis Core polyglot monorepo. Listing each
// Go module here lets `go fmt ./...`, `go vet ./...`, and other tooling
// invoked from the repo root descend into every module at once.
//
// Bazel + rules_go is the authoritative build system (per ADR-0009);
// this file exists only so the hermetic Go SDK wrapper in
// `tools/scripts/go.sh` can resolve module paths like `./gateway_go/...`
// without requiring contributors to cd into each module first.
//
// Keep this file in sync with the top-level Go module directories.

go 1.24

use (
	./gateway_go
)
